{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"f231fb4c-8644-4f92-9a22-f8eb0636ef19","content":"`.testsettings` files are **not supported** by modern MSTest (v3+). You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your file configures and how each setting maps:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout` property | `<TestTimeout>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| Code coverage data collector | `<DataCollector>` in `<DataCollectionRunSettings>` |\n| `AssemblyResolution` / deployment | No longer needed (SDK-style projects handle this automatically) |\n\nLet me create the `.runsettings` file and update your project:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_015HzvxcjyVboNdB8mecYG94","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01ATfKKd5WWj9aeYmPoPytED","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-7ad70872d4254e08a1cdf87890c7554b/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.SingleFileCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral\" />\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-7ad70872d4254e08a1cdf87890c7554b/local.runsettings."},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01SeBRyX1VFpf1aTmgC2XArz","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-7ad70872d4254e08a1cdf87890c7554b/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>","new_str":"  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n    <RunSettingsFilePath>$(MSBuildProjectDirectory)\\local.runsettings</RunSettingsFilePath>\n  </PropertyGroup>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-7ad70872d4254e08a1cdf87890c7554b/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"9c584c82-86a5-429c-ad08-c489971f2e2b","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file which is the legacy format. Modern MSTest (v3+) uses `.runsettings` files instead. I need to help them migrate from `.testsettings` to `.runsettings`.\n\nThe `.testsettings` file contains:\n1. Assembly resolution with `useLoadContext=\"true\"`\n2. A test timeout of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. A code coverage data collector\n\nLet me create the equivalent `.runsettings` file and update the `.csproj` to reference it.","outputTokens":791,"requestId":"4812:5465:8CB55:A28C7:69FBFACA"},"id":"b065852a-a23f-43b3-8597-7c738bcb389e","timestamp":"2026-05-07T02:37:09.161Z","parentId":"5d8d36f8-373c-402c-92c7-bf2067eb6511"}
